Deploy your code What is an application An application is defined on Clever Cloud by the following elements:
a dedicated language/framework a deployment method (FTP and/or Git) RAM and CPU consumption, depending on the language or framework used an optional configuration file you may add to your project If one of these elements is missing, Clever Cloud can&rsquo;t deploy your application properly (except the configuration file, optional in some cases).

